ries, veins, and microscopic vessels. Blood clots can cause life-threatening events like strokes. And, in COVID-19, microscopic clots may restrict blood flow in the lungs, impairing oxygen exchange.<br />\n<br />\n驗屍睇有冇抗體同血栓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知會唔會極速燒屍"}}